{"word":"κρυπτεύω","slug":"κρυπτεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κρυπτεύω</b></el> <el>(κρυπτεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κρύπτω'><el>κρύπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to conceal, hide</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>intrans, <i>to hide oneself, lie concealed</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be ensnared</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}